{"tid":1824114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"批鬥撚=分化撚   必須死全家","createTime":"2020-01-14T08:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:53:35.000Z","uid":49083,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1151334df56585b0cace187aa5be0ce94cceaab5","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:05:24.000Z","msg":"唔講真係以為抗爭者有好多人，但事實上有做野的已經好少。事實黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經少人架啦....大家批鬥自己人，不停話邊個黃D，邊個唔夠黃，係唔係唔記得左敵人係邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好多時間好好打？花資源搞自己友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃店唔夠黃要當藍？你痴撚線呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n子華唔夠黃？因為佢呢幾個月無開大咪屌政府？你又做左咩？食左龍門？好威好黃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍門經濟圈定黃色經濟圈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母呀批鬥撚，批鬥撚你根本同阻膠一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔敢對極權出手，為左顯示自己存在就對自己人出手，行為低劣無恥同狗一樣。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n欺善怕惡，屌你老母。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ad1b4f690329668bedc14a8bf0a6dfdce57291","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"對家派少少打手就偷走曬你地集中力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58016ff4236dad69cadfe045c052356c8f7e7fda","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人又唔多, 重批鬥手足...."},{"pid":"97209d5770d1143ec74fe3bee836c6f7abb20a78","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"明明手足一日幾個, 都玩內鬥<br />\n此風不可長"},{"pid":"c65b433f82581a5742470671b12280a72ed33f18","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97209d5770d1143ec74fe3bee836c6f7abb20a78","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"明明手足一日幾個, 都玩內鬥<br />\n此風不可長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"一日少幾個"},{"pid":"4146f48d03f7dad0c558ecac52ac516c9ed5eb29","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f749f42622ed7a956da81b934c4d2633092dfe7d","tid":1824114,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"反批鬥力量<img src=\"/assets/faces